	bool "Support for Olivetti M700-10"
	depends on MACH_JAZZ
	select DMA_NONCOHERENT
	select SYS_SUPPORTS_LITTLE_ENDIAN
	help
	  This is a machine with a R4000 100 MHz CPU. To compile a Beep
	  kernel that runs on these, say Y here. For details about Beep on
	  the MIPS architecture, check out the Beep/MIPS FAQ on the WWW at
	  <http://www.beep-mips.org/>.
